It also provides sustainable, barrier, label, CPP, and paper lamination films, and cast polypropylene products. Its products are used for food packaging; tobacco and box overwraps; anti-fog bags for vegetables, fresh fruits, and salad; paper look packaging and paper lamination; clear, white, and metallized label packaging; and ice cream, candy, and soap packaging. It also involved in investment, trading, import, export, distribution, and other activities. PT Trias Sentosa Tbk was founded in 1979 and is based in Sidoarjo, Indonesia.

info.address2: 3rd Floor Jalan Raya Halim Perdanakusuma
info.longBusinessSummary: PT Cardig Aero Services Tbk, together with its subsidiaries, provides ground and cargo handling, aircraft release and maintenance, catering, facility management, and aviation training services in Indonesia. The company offers passenger handling, including baggage and aircraft handling, ground support equipment usage, operation of business class lounge, and special assistance services; cargo buildup and breakdown, cargo documentation, cargo transfer and transit handling, cargo storage, and special cargo handling services; and repair and maintenance service for air transportation vehicles. It also provides food and catering services, as well as housekeeping, laundry, gardening, accommodation, transportation, and other services; and flight simulators to aircraft pilots and other training services. In addition, the company engages in airport management; restaurant business; and investment activities. PT Cardig Aero Services Tbk was founded in 1984 and is headquartered in Jakarta, Indonesia.

info.longBusinessSummary: PT Berlina Tbk, together with its subsidiaries, manufactures plastic for packaging in Indonesia and internationally. The company offers laminated tubes, plastic coextrusion tubes, toothbrushes, moulds, and plastic packaging components. It also provides blow moulding, blown film, injection moulding, injection stretch blow moulding, injection blow moulding, decoration, mould shop, mini tube, plastic tube, and thermo forming products and services. In addition, the company engages in plastic processing, general trading, and service activities. It primarily serves multinational companies in various industries, including cosmetics, pharmaceuticals, food and beverage, industrial goods, etc. The company was founded in 1969 and is headquartered in Bekasi, Indonesia. The company is a subsidiary of PT Dwi Satrya Utama.
